        <body>
            <div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><head><anchor xml:id="xmlid__heading_h_2s8eyo1"/><hi rend="baseline">İSTM.ŞSC.14.d.400 / 55a-1_</hi><ref target="http://document__41"><hi rend="baseline underline color(1155cc)">GrocerIST id_40</hi></ref></head><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Mahrūse-i Galata tevābi’nden kasaba-i Beşiktaşa tābi‘ Arnavud karyesinde mütemekkin iken bundan akdem hālik olan Bakkāl Astati veled-i Yaninin verāseti zevcesi Perapyon bt. [] ve sulbī sagīr oğulları Yani ve Yanko ve sulbī kebīr oğlu Mimive sulbiye sagīre kızı [] münhasıra olduğu şer‘an zāhir oldukdan sonra sıgār-ı mesfūrunun tesviye-i emrlerine kıbel-i şer‘-i enverden vāsi nasb olunan mesfūre Perapyon ve mesfūr Mimi taleb ve iltimāslarıyla tahrīr olunan tereke-i hālik mesfūrdur ki ber vech-i ātī zikr olunur. Fī 24 Zilka‘de 1183</hi>  </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Evānī-i nuhāsiye:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 3960</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold background(white)" xml:space="preserve">Yün: </hi><hi rend="background(white)">Kıyye 60 / Kıymet 1080</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Minder gılıfı:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kilim hasır:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 360</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Yorgan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 4 / 1200</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Yanbolu kebesi:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 2 / 540</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Şamdan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 60</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Şalvar:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 240</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kuşak:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 500</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Gömlek:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 150</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold background(yellow)" xml:space="preserve">.. </hi><hi rend="bold">kebesi:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 300</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold" xml:space="preserve">Hırdavat: </hi><hi>300</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Nakd der kīse:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 2790</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold" xml:space="preserve">Hamr müdre: </hi><hi>Aded 150 / Kıymet 18000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold" xml:space="preserve">Arak müdresi: </hi><hi>Aded 45 / 9390</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Varil, fuçı, potna:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> 1800</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi xml:space="preserve">Hālik mefsūrun karye-i mezbūrede vāki‘ bakkāl dükkānında mevcūd eşyāsıdır ki zikr olunur: </hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Pekmez:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 900</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Nardenk:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 96</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Asel:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 200</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Revgan-ı sāde:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 280</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Revgan-ı zeyt:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 5400</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Sirke:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 390</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Soğan:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 120</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Tuzlu balık:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 420</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Üzüm:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 90</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Tulum peyniri:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 336</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Mum:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 440</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Bastırma:</hi> <hi>Kıymet 54</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Kaşkaval peyniri:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 2250</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold">Pirinç:</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> Kıymet 660</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi rend="bold" xml:space="preserve">Destgāh hırdavat: </hi><hi>Kıymet 1750</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Zikr olunan bakkāl dükkānında iki terāzū ma derāhim ve beş tabla ve iki kantar vesāir beyne’l-esnāf gedik ta‘bīr olunur eşya ber verch-i tahmīn: 24000</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Hālik mesfūrun karye-i mezkūrede vāki‘ lede’l-ahālī ve’l-cīrān ma‘lūmü’l-hudūd ve’l-müştemilāt mülk menzili kıymeti ber vech-i tahmīn: 66000</hi> </p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi xml:space="preserve">Hālik mesfūrun karye-i mezkūrede </hi><hi rend="background(white)">bağları hilalinde</hi><hi xml:space="preserve"> vāki‘ </hi><hi style="font-size:8.5pt"> </hi><hi>kürūmī bir kıt’a bağı kıymeti ber vech-i tahmīn: 14400</hi></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><hi>Hālik mesfūrun karye-i mezkūrede vāki‘ kürūmī mülk bağı kıymeti ber vech-i tahmīn: meblağ: 10800</hi></p></div>
